<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <title>🎉 Fun Dashboard</title>
  <link
    href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@300;400;600&display=swap"
    rel="stylesheet"
  />
  <style>
    :root {
      --sunny: #ffdd57;
      --sky:   #57c7ff;
      --grass: #6bef8c;
      --cloud: #ffffff;
      --text:  #333;
      --radius: 1rem;
      --shadow: rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
    }
    *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
    body {
      font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
      background: linear-gradient(to bottom, var(--sky), var(--grass));
      min-height: 100vh;
      color: var(--text);
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
      padding-bottom: 2rem;
      animation: floatIn 1s ease-out both;
    }
    header {
      width: 100%;
      max-width: 800px;
      margin-top: 2rem;
      padding: 1rem 2rem;
      background: var(--sunny);
      border-radius: var(--radius);
      box-shadow: 0 4px 12px var(--shadow);
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
      animation: wiggle 2s infinite;
    }
    header h1 { font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: 600; }
    header .user-info a { color: inherit; text-decoration: underline; }
    main {
      width: 100%;
      max-width: 800px;
      margin-top: 2rem;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .hero {
      background: var(--cloud);
      border-radius: var(--radius);
      padding: 2.5rem 1.5rem;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 12px var(--shadow);
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
      animation: pop 0.8s ease-out;
    }
    .hero svg {
      position: absolute;
      bottom: -20px; left: -20px;
      width: 120px; opacity: 0.1;
    }
    .hero h2 {
      font-size: 1.8rem;
      margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
      color: var(--sky);
    }
    .hero p {
      font-size: 1rem;
      color: var(--text);
      line-height: 1.4;
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }
    .cards {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(180px, 1fr));
      gap: 1.5rem;
    }
    .card {
      background: var(--cloud);
      border-radius: var(--radius);
      padding: 1.5rem;
      box-shadow: 0 2px 8px var(--shadow);
      transition: transform 0.3s, box-shadow 0.3s;
      position: relative;
    }
    .card:hover {
      transform: translateY(-6px) rotate(-1deg);
      box-shadow: 0 8px 16px var(--shadow);
    }
    .card h3 {
      margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
      font-size: 1.2rem;
      color: var(--sky);
    }
    .card p {
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      color: var(--text);
      line-height: 1.3;
    }

    @keyframes floatIn {
      from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(20px); }
      to   { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
    }
    @keyframes pop {
      0%   { transform: scale(0.9); opacity: 0; }
      60%  { transform: scale(1.05); opacity: 1; }
      100% { transform: scale(1); }
    }
    @keyframes wiggle {
      0%,100% { transform: rotate(0); }
      25%      { transform: rotate(1deg); }
      75%      { transform: rotate(-1deg); }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <header>
    <h1>👋 Hey, <%= name %>!</h1>
    <div class="user-info">
      <%= email %> | <a href="/mypage/logout">Log out</a>
    </div>
  </header>

  <main>
    <!-- Hero Funny Message -->
    <section class="hero">
      <svg viewBox="0 0 100 100">
        <circle cx="50" cy="50" r="50" fill="var(--sky)" />
      </svg>
      <h2>Whatcha Lookin’ At?</h2>
      <p>
        Welcome to the world’s most delightful dashboard! No boring stats here—only guaranteed giggles, spontaneous smiles, and the occasional existential thought about coffee ☕. Sit back, relax, and enjoy the ride!
      </p>
    </section>

    <!-- Joke Cards -->
    <div class="cards">
      

    <div class="card">
  <h3>Why did the database administrator leave his wife?</h3>
  <p>She had one-to-many relationships. 💔🔗</p>
</div>
<div class="card">
  <h3>Why was the JavaScript developer sad?</h3>
  <p>Because he didn’t Node how to Express himself. 😢📦</p>
</div>
<div class="card">
  <h3>“You’re the CSS to my HTML—bringing style to my structure.”</h3>
  <p>Without you, I’m just plain text. 📝✨</p>
</div>

      <div class="card">
  <h3>“Even the Taj Mahal wasn’t built in a day—🏰✨”</h3>
  <p>🔨 Grab your chisel and start chiseling your dreams! 💭🚀</p>
</div>

    </div>
  </main>

</body>
</html>
